Package: passtime
Title: Power and Sample Size for Time Course Microarray Experiments
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Joanne", "Beer", , "joannecbeer@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The passtime package does power and sample size analysis 
    for time course microarray differential expression experimental designs 
    via Monte Carlo simulations. Uses R package snowfall for parallel computing.
Suggests: snowfall
Depends: R (>= 3.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
